function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 510') {
	err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.0.510!');
}

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

if (!is_file('TODO')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: TODO');
	writefile_1();
	if (!is_file('TODO')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): TODO');
	} else if (sha1_file('TODO') != '8c99739385e5a10eeb031bc1ed9538050252ada4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): TODO');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('TODO', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of TODO');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '8c99739385e5a10eeb031bc1ed9538050252ada4') {
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== 'e39942e40aef308338e9e885322eb009ace680d8') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: TODO');
			$tmp = pathinfo('TODO');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('TODO')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('TODO', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_1();
		if (@sha1_file('TODO') !== '8c99739385e5a10eeb031bc1ed9538050252ada4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): TODO');
		}
	}
}

}
if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	writefile_17();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') != '62660fe35f5ccb033ef3d5b8951bd8ce7f04fc2c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== '62660fe35f5ccb033ef3d5b8951bd8ce7f04fc2c') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== 'dabf90f8f3af6f7ef750d4b3a892e04b15f467f8') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_17();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_access') !== '62660fe35f5ccb033ef3d5b8951bd8ce7f04fc2c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_access');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	writefile_18();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') != '3290dcfe1634802656662a57bdfcca6828c2fead') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '3290dcfe1634802656662a57bdfcca6828c2fead') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '9ec3eebfb93c8b0b1362ec89ee99d881f2f4f8bc') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_18();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql') !== '3290dcfe1634802656662a57bdfcca6828c2fead') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mssql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	writefile_19();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') != '7c01dbbb9ee5e051a12de4bb670e308db7905328') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== '7c01dbbb9ee5e051a12de4bb670e308db7905328') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== '5d2486d9677f40a776504745e7e56bd910f057b3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_19();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql') !== '7c01dbbb9ee5e051a12de4bb670e308db7905328') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_mysql');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	writefile_20();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') != '9be14b1a8d55ff4ada202ac4af280db9c085a7ed') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '9be14b1a8d55ff4ada202ac4af280db9c085a7ed') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '5187b2d5006aa398b628aae989ba11c1bb792505') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_20();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql') !== '9be14b1a8d55ff4ada202ac4af280db9c085a7ed') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_pgsql');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_21();
	if (!is_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') != '07dd30456755178044b3fa05a30775b45fe0369d') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== '07dd30456755178044b3fa05a30775b45fe0369d') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== 'a06473c8d8dcdf18581a6b1c7b1367fb261fbbbf') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_21();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite') !== '07dd30456755178044b3fa05a30775b45fe0369d') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/generate_wellknown_other_sqlite');
		}
	}
}

	writefile_23();
	if (!is_file('dev/oidinfo_add_missing')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/oidinfo_add_missing');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/oidinfo_add_missing') != 'ef2a8dea63ab8fc191646fa78a132e2359e37a14') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/oidinfo_add_missing');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/oidinfo_add_missing', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/oidinfo_add_missing');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/oidinfo_add_missing') !== 'ef2a8dea63ab8fc191646fa78a132e2359e37a14') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/oidinfo_add_missing') !== '5485c50cfca95c46f3b9062449afe3cc4cce1bf1') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/oidinfo_add_missing');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/oidinfo_add_missing');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/oidinfo_add_missing')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/oidinfo_add_missing', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_23();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/oidinfo_add_missing') !== 'ef2a8dea63ab8fc191646fa78a132e2359e37a14') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/oidinfo_add_missing');
		}
	}
}

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('ZGF0YSkgeyAvLyBnZXQgMzEgYml0cyBmcm9tIFNIQTEuIFZhbHVlcyAwLi4yMTQ3NDgzNjQ3CglyZXR1cm4gKGhleGRlYyhzdWJzdHIoc2hhMSgkZGF0YSksLTQqMikpICYgMjE0NzQ4MzY0Nyk7Cn0KCg=='));
	@fclose($fp);
}
if (!is_file('dev/systemid_collider')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/systemid_collider');
	writefile_31();
	if (!is_file('dev/systemid_collider')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/systemid_collider');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/systemid_collider') != '402a3021542d0434007a23e120a5f2717e06cb8c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/systemid_collider');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/systemid_collider', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/systemid_collider');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/systemid_collider') !== '402a3021542d0434007a23e120a5f2717e06cb8c') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/systemid_collider') !== 'fa3088b41ef150a50698b95bca4b826699874a59') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/systemid_collider');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/systemid_collider');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/systemid_collider')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/systemid_collider', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_31();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/systemid_collider') !== '402a3021542d0434007a23e120a5f2717e06cb8c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/systemid_collider');
		}
	}
}

}
if (!is_file('dev/test_database_plugins')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/test_database_plugins');
	writefile_32();
	if (!is_file('dev/test_database_plugins')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/test_database_plugins');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') != 'b86455184be2b97d74ae49ee7fe61ca2c7fe3eeb') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/test_database_plugins');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/test_database_plugins', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/test_database_plugins');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') !== 'b86455184be2b97d74ae49ee7fe61ca2c7fe3eeb') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') !== '985c82c545d6d96905251b83c94550a998546f00') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/test_database_plugins');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/test_database_plugins');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/test_database_plugins')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/test_database_plugins', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_32();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/test_database_plugins') !== 'b86455184be2b97d74ae49ee7fe61ca2c7fe3eeb') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/test_database_plugins');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	writefile_36();
	if (!is_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') != '646098701a988ca29c60e10c348e8cf9c5b81585') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') !== '646098701a988ca29c60e10c348e8cf9c5b81585') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') !== 'aa4738ea4a1198d8e9a33ed917e1f86202e398ea') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_36();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps') !== '646098701a988ca29c60e10c348e8cf9c5b81585') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/generate_proof_files.phps');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	writefile_37();
	if (!is_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	} else if (sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') != '7b8b5a21e17f2ee9a28cb90f4bb0d45b19885818') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', 0755)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== '7b8b5a21e17f2ee9a28cb90f4bb0d45b19885818') {
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== '67b1bdf767aeb60443e30a12e0a3f88a191fd0f5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
			$tmp = pathinfo('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_37();
		if (@sha1_file('dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps') !== '7b8b5a21e17f2ee9a28cb90f4bb0d45b19885818') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): dev/translation/message_regenerate.phps');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_41();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != '2bc8f1ca7a810d231222dd97ebe4eb5addc18911') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '2bc8f1ca7a810d231222dd97ebe4eb5addc18911') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== 'cebce210a6815fd87804961e41c315813e67c4f6') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_41();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== '2bc8f1ca7a810d231222dd97ebe4eb5addc18911') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	writefile_59();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') != 'b502f6cebb98a4161a7316175f59d85c055af31f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'b502f6cebb98a4161a7316175f59d85c055af31f') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'f708fe4ce9608c9a7566badb40ad803c92583081') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_59();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php') !== 'b502f6cebb98a4161a7316175f59d85c055af31f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusMenuUtils.class.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php') != '1ccf981e32d112478b20bb840925049a43bfb93f') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php') !== '1ccf981e32d112478b20bb840925049a43bfb93f') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php') !== 'bf44fca9fdd4d7086aaaf68b0a08e0e36557260d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_71();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php') !== '1ccf981e32d112478b20bb840925049a43bfb93f') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusSQLException.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php');
	writefile_79();
	if (!is_file('includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php') != 'e6a85a455026a615229ff89439020249b2f38129') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php') !== 'e6a85a455026a615229ff89439020249b2f38129') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php') !== '2ce74c84d1e5844de3b1888cd6779ab47b0b8c0b') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_79();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php') !== 'e6a85a455026a615229ff89439020249b2f38129') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/db_updates/update204.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/functions.inc.php');
	writefile_80();
	if (!is_file('includes/functions.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') != 'b27cb3c28e30866f6f3d322176cda92578790ab4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/functions.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/functions.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== 'b27cb3c28e30866f6f3d322176cda92578790ab4') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== '3939b9fdbfeda41b600d40b2534764567b0a70a9') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/functions.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/functions.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/functions.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/functions.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_80();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/functions.inc.php') !== 'b27cb3c28e30866f6f3d322176cda92578790ab4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/functions.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	writefile_81();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') != 'aeb911b456af16f1bd3e877f11174f9cdcd9f2e8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidplus.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidplus.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== 'aeb911b456af16f1bd3e877f11174f9cdcd9f2e8') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== 'd36c3f45166c2f17db67f958a5286725120de40e') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidplus.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidplus.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidplus.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidplus.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_81();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus.inc.php') !== 'aeb911b456af16f1bd3e877f11174f9cdcd9f2e8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oidplus_base.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidplus_base.js');
	writefile_82();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidplus_base.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidplus_base.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidplus_base.js') != '12df79fd6905a7bd2ceda05e49a49a88a70e2d02') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus_base.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidplus_base.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidplus_base.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_base.js') !== '12df79fd6905a7bd2ceda05e49a49a88a70e2d02') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_base.js') !== 'cc9688dc06f71e733a101c6b22431c94061bbb30') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidplus_base.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidplus_base.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidplus_base.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidplus_base.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_82();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_base.js') !== '12df79fd6905a7bd2ceda05e49a49a88a70e2d02') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus_base.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
	writefile_83();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php') != '4c521984b3a01373386427778a0ac90860398482') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php') !== '4c521984b3a01373386427778a0ac90860398482') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php') !== '36846279e1368e76c98de6bc8e4e7081c34da787') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_83();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php') !== '4c521984b3a01373386427778a0ac90860398482') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus_dependency.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php');
	writefile_84();
	if (!is_file('includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php') != '545862c0920d24542637660eb40049db175740b4') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php') !== '545862c0920d24542637660eb40049db175740b4') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php') !== 'd61d9aa55e4454ce5825d3812a2eb5cfbebda402') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_84();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php') !== '545862c0920d24542637660eb40049db175740b4') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/oidplus_limits.inc.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: index.php');
	writefile_85();
	if (!is_file('index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('index.php') != 'c50a1c07caa013841317ab780fe3b12abbe2b58c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== 'c50a1c07caa013841317ab780fe3b12abbe2b58c') {
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== 'dd09276654d35dadffe0a3f9e8ca7c082327bb4c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_85();
		if (@sha1_file('index.php') !== 'c50a1c07caa013841317ab780fe3b12abbe2b58c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): index.php');
		}
	}
}

	if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') !== '81e2d3de26e79bab68046c691e1d88f543a4694a') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') !== 'c107b2a5857e604450bb13774d1760a77196d7aa') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_105();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js') !== '81e2d3de26e79bab68046c691e1d88f543a4694a') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/adminPages/700_colors/OIDplusPageAdminColors.js');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php');
	writefile_118();
	if (!is_file('plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php') != '485ba625fed00578d00f1191007b129ea965f05c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php') !== '485ba625fed00578d00f1191007b129ea965f05c') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php') !== 'bd20ace617e6c0956ea656e83f8976275be75bc5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php');

			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_118();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php') !== '485ba625fed00578d00f1191007b129ea965f05c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/odbc/OIDplusDatabasePluginODBC.class.php');
		}
	}

	writefile_124();

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/database/pdo/OIDplusQueryResultPDO.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/OIDplusQueryResultPDO.class.php') != '05f70747293c5076dcb9a742591d8523ba9cabee') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/database/pdo/OIDplusQueryResultPDO.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/database/pdo/OIDplusQueryResultPDO.class.php', 0644)) {

	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/OIDplusQueryResultPDO.class.php') !== '05f70747293c5076dcb9a742591d8523ba9cabee') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/OIDplusQueryResultPDO.class.php') !== '1f3aaca1ff4c95835c0e2e4fc225cca342aea342') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/database/pdo/OIDplusQueryResultPDO.class.php');

			if (!@copy('plugins/database/pdo/OIDplusQueryResultPDO.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/database/pdo/OIDplusQueryResultPDO.class.php') !== '05f70747293c5076dcb9a742591d8523ba9cabee') {

if (!is_file('plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php');
	writefile_133();
	if (!is_file('plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php') != '1b96fb2d24bfc793a10d9d1daec7ca31468c0334') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php') !== '1b96fb2d24bfc793a10d9d1daec7ca31468c0334') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php') !== 'c87dcdb9ad97dc622d9fb35ae406f64c4d1f40bb') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_133();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php') !== '1b96fb2d24bfc793a10d9d1daec7ca31468c0334') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/design/default/OIDplusDesignPluginDefault.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css');
	writefile_134();
	if (!is_file('plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css') != '89b5e5f34fec735904994268aa9e662b0702b039') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css') !== '89b5e5f34fec735904994268aa9e662b0702b039') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css') !== '437b786eec76958bc1928608943b3e7f29602db8') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_134();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css') !== '89b5e5f34fec735904994268aa9e662b0702b039') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/design/default/oidplus_base.css');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php');
	writefile_135();
	if (!is_file('plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php') != '792602bbbcffd3455639df53f694d20462eb133b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php') !== '792602bbbcffd3455639df53f694d20462eb133b') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php') !== '3d93ce6732384fb565786d8fb323a0816f92c859') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_135();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php') !== '792602bbbcffd3455639df53f694d20462eb133b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/design/ironbase/OIDplusDesignPluginIronBase.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	writefile_178();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') != '6d2e702dc8f948a5a50ce50e13ebaa590142865c') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== '6d2e702dc8f948a5a50ce50e13ebaa590142865c') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== 'e8e298583efda4a8fc0af0523ecf5ebdb2c129dd') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_178();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php') !== '6d2e702dc8f948a5a50ce50e13ebaa590142865c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/100_whois/whois/webwhois.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js');
	writefile_180();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js') != '38816fe9fb203dc85352d385c5d71321abe2bff2') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js') !== '38816fe9fb203dc85352d385c5d71321abe2bff2') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js') !== 'f94ea2f58992712cb2c90a0afe94146bacc4dc2c') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js');

			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_180();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js') !== '38816fe9fb203dc85352d385c5d71321abe2bff2') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/200_viathinksoft_freeoid/OIDplusPagePublicFreeOID.js');

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	writefile_183();
	if (!is_file('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') != '334aee14850cfa60230e91da633d97a79f915639') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '334aee14850cfa60230e91da633d97a79f915639') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '0c3d8b3170b38b931521f9a3288f105605f15f07') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_183();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php') !== '334aee14850cfa60230e91da633d97a79f915639') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/publicPages/500_resources/show_icon.php');
		}
	}

	if (!is_file('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php') != '2dbfcec24e7a4256282b025fa392b625f5544f16') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php') !== '2dbfcec24e7a4256282b025fa392b625f5544f16') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php') !== 'abcf5c891884d43d04bc4ce445c017fdb913623f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_207();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php') !== '2dbfcec24e7a4256282b025fa392b625f5544f16') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/sqlSlang/sqlite/OIDplusSqlSlangPluginSQLite.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	writefile_210();
	if (!is_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') != 'f8b65da419a8ed37402ffb729080850c74f40a73') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/includes/setup_base.js', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/includes/setup_base.js');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') !== 'f8b65da419a8ed37402ffb729080850c74f40a73') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') !== '91342760d96ac31d4a59b4381ce7bb17a03ba3f0') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/includes/setup_base.js');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/includes/setup_base.js');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/includes/setup_base.js')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/includes/setup_base.js', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_210();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/includes/setup_base.js') !== 'f8b65da419a8ed37402ffb729080850c74f40a73') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/includes/setup_base.js');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/index.php');
	writefile_211();
	if (!is_file('setup/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/index.php') != '265561329ba7fe446f8fd6b6753459c2fc115b33') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== '265561329ba7fe446f8fd6b6753459c2fc115b33') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== '527d0c398dea1c69f95af8180bd1f3e30cabbd79') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_211();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/index.php') !== '265561329ba7fe446f8fd6b6753459c2fc115b33') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/index.php');
		}
	}
}

// Files different: setup/setup.min.css.php

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: setup/setup.min.css.php');
	writefile_212();
	if (!is_file('setup/setup.min.css.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): setup/setup.min.css.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('setup/setup.min.css.php') != '71d4d199a120aa615e16753c7040e6dd505758c8') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): setup/setup.min.css.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('setup/setup.min.css.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of setup/setup.min.css.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('setup/setup.min.css.php') !== '71d4d199a120aa615e16753c7040e6dd505758c8') {
		if (@sha1_file('setup/setup.min.css.php') !== '6f284133ad5bbbc258e4e2e6dee11cae20b7889d') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: setup/setup.min.css.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('setup/setup.min.css.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('setup/setup.min.css.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('setup/setup.min.css.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_212();
		if (@sha1_file('setup/setup.min.css.php') !== '71d4d199a120aa615e16753c7040e6dd505758c8') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): setup/setup.min.css.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('update/index.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: update/index.php');
	writefile_219();
	if (!is_file('update/index.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): update/index.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('update/index.php') != '85bffbd091cd5fa61cb1343eb613bcea2afc5131') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): update/index.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('update/index.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of update/index.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== '85bffbd091cd5fa61cb1343eb613bcea2afc5131') {
		if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== '3845646cc64806636fdc1d3f64fbad86f730efa5') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: update/index.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('update/index.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('update/index.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('update/index.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_219();
		if (@sha1_file('update/index.php') !== '85bffbd091cd5fa61cb1343eb613bcea2afc5131') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): update/index.php');
		}
	}
}


file_put_contents('oidplus_version.txt', "Revision 511\n");
if (trim(@file_get_contents('oidplus_version.txt')) !== 'Revision 511') err('Could not write to oidplus_version.txt!');


echo 'DONE'; // This exact string will be compared in Update v3

@unlink(__FILE__);
if (is_file(__FILE__)) warn('Could not delete '.basename(__FILE__).'! Please delete it manually');
